data.comment: The whistle has gone to start the match.
Free kick Falkenbergs.
In the minute 3, Karl Soderstrom gets his shot on target but fails to score for Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In Uppsala, Nsima Peter (Falkenbergs) misses the target with a header.
In the minute 4, Goal kick for Sirius at Studenternas IP.
Yukiya Sugita (Sirius) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Corner awarded to Sirius.
In the minute 8, Corner awarded to Sirius.
Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
Can Falkenbergs get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Sirius's half?
In the minute 10, It's a goal kick for the home team in Uppsala.
Sirius have a dangerous throw-in.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 12, Free kick for Sirius in their own half.
Fredrik Klitte awards the away team a throw-in.
Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
In the minute 13, Sirius's Adam Hellborg has been booked in Uppsala.
Corner awarded to Sirius.
Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Sirius in their own half.

Play has been interrupted briefly in Uppsala to check on Hjalmar Ekdal, who is grimacing with pain.
Sirius have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 22, Fredrik Klitte signals a Sirius throw-in in Falkenbergs's half.
Hjalmar Ekdal returns to the field for Sirius after picking up a slight injury.
In Uppsala a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 25, Corner awarded to Sirius.

In the minute 27, Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Falkenbergs.
Free kick for Falkenbergs in their own half.
Throw-in Sirius.
In the minute 29, Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
Sirius to take a throw-in in Falkenbergs territory.
Free kick for Sirius in the half of Falkenbergs.
In the minute 33, In Uppsala, Stefano Vecchia (Sirius) gets his head to the ball but the strike is cleared by an untiring defence.
At Studenternas IP, Falkenbergs are penalized for being offside.
Sirius drives forward and Stefano Vecchia gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In the minute 35, Falkenbergs's Tobias Englund breaks free at Studenternas IP. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Falkenbergs.
In the minute 37, Throw-in for Sirius at Studenternas IP.
In Uppsala, Stefano Vecchia of Sirius is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
Sirius have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 40, Free kick for Falkenbergs in the half of Sirius.
Fredrik Klitte awards Sirius a goal kick.
Sirius's Stefano Vecchia gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Falkenbergs defender.
In the minute 41, Corner awarded to Sirius.
Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Sirius territory.
In the minute 43, Throw-in for Sirius in their own half.
Free kick Falkenbergs.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Uppsala.
In the minute 45, In Uppsala a free kick has been awarded the home team.
2 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
In the minute 45, The first half has been concluded at Studenternas IP.
At Studenternas IP, John Bjorkengren has been yellow-carded for the away team.
The second half has started at Studenternas IP.
Fredrik Klitte signals a Falkenbergs throw-in in Sirius's half.
In the minute 47, Falkenbergs's Edi Sylisufaj is on target but unsuccessful.
Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 50, Sirius's Yukiya Sugita gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Ball goes out of play for a Falkenbergs goal kick.
Tibor Joza is on a sub for Karl Soderstrom for Falkenbergs.
In the minute 51, Fredrik Klitte awards Sirius a goal kick.
Throw-in for Sirius in the half of Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 53, Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
Sirius are pushing forward but Adam Stahl's finish is wide of the goal.
Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
In the minute 56, Sirius pushes forward through Nahom Girmai, whose finish on goal is saved.
Ball safe as Falkenbergs is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Sirius have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 62, Sirius drive upfield and Axel Bjornstrom gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Falkenbergs defender.
Yukiya Sugita (Sirius) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Corner awarded to Sirius.

Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Studenternas IP.
Free kick for Sirius in their own half.

Henrik Rydstrom (Sirius) is making a first substitution, with Laorent Shabani replacing Adam Hellborg.
Tobias Englund is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
In the minute 67, Sirius are whistled for offside.
Tobias Englund for Falkenbergs is back on the field again.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 68, Goal! Elias Andersson gives Sirius a 1-0 lead in Uppsala.
Yukiya Sugita instrumental with a fine assist.
Can Falkenbergs get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Sirius's half?
In the minute 70, Throw-in for Falkenbergs close to the penalty box.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Sirius territory.
In the minute 73, Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
Important block from the Sirius defence as Carl Johansson fires in a strike for Falkenbergs.
In the minute 74, Can Sirius get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Falkenbergs's half?
Ball safe as Falkenbergs is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 75, Throw-in for Falkenbergs at Studenternas IP.
Anton Wede (Falkenbergs) has replaced the possibly injured Tobias Englund at Studenternas IP.
In Uppsala a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Goal! Stefano Vecchia extends Sirius's lead to 2-0.
In the minute 77, Great play from Adam Stahl to set up the goal.
Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Falkenbergs.
Fredrik Klitte awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 80, Fredrik Klitte signals a free kick to Sirius in their own half.
Tibor Joza for Falkenbergs has been booked by Fredrik Klitte and receives a first yellow card.
The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Lukas Jonsson.
In the minute 82, Lukas Jonsson is back on his feet again.
Fredrik Klitte signals a Sirius throw-in in Falkenbergs's half.
Lukas Jonsson (Sirius) has received a yellow card from Fredrik Klitte.
In the minute 83, Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Sirius have a goal kick.
In the minute 84, Edi Sylisufaj keeps the away team in the match by reducing the deficit to 2-1.
Johan Karlsson is replacing Elias Andersson for Sirius at Studenternas IP.
The away team replace Christoffer Carlsson with John Chibuike.
In the minute 86, Throw-in for Falkenbergs in the half of Sirius.
Sirius awarded a free kick in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
In the minute 89, Throw-in for Sirius in the half of Falkenbergs.
Free kick Falkenbergs.
At Studenternas IP the fourth official shows that 6 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Uppsala.
In Uppsala Falkenbergs drive forward through Nsima Peter. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Axel Noren (Falkenbergs) gets in a powerful header but the ball is cleared away.
Sirius push upfield but Fredrik Klitte quickly pulls them for offside.
Johan Karlsson of Sirius smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Sirius have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
Can Falkenbergs capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Fredrik Klitte blows to end the match. The final score is 2-1.
The home team have replaced Yukiya Sugita with Niklas Busch Thor. This is the second substitution made today by Henrik Rydstrom.
